Max wis first.<br>
Git AGL ta 75.<br>
Den rest ta STA.<br>
<br>
Ya max wis wit an Ogah shammy issa 101 me thinks.  Only stat da matters dat ya can't buff.<br>
Ogah's got crappy AGL, git it above 75 ta avoids da big AC hit.<br>
Bace Ogah STA issa 120 iffa I remember rights, so it not assa big a deal puttin points inta it.<br>
Unlike melee, shammies are casters anda git a really poor return onna STA ta HP afta 200.  Mah STA onna Grubb issa 245 wit self buffs.  When I drop it ta 205 I can't see any difference inna mah red bar.  Wis fer mana anda HP items willa take ya farther me feels.  Fer shammy gear git a Rune Etched Icewurm Fang, Fungi Tunic, da standard 6ac/65hp rings, anda what eva chain anda shield ya kin afford.  Ya kin git ta 54th wearin full totemic wit outs too much hassle, any gear betta den dat jus it fasta.<br>
